text: Lê Xuân Anh (born 26 July 1991) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a defender for V-League (Vietnam) club Thanh Hóa. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:FLC Thanh Hóa F.C. players Category:Hai Phong F.C. players Category:V.League 1 players Category:People from Thanh Hóa Province
